<lyrics>[V1]
 1. I hinnau Lalpen chuh I na he puou in,
 Tuhin muh di'n a um hi;
 I Pau kumkhuo a I hawl uh I he puou,
 A hihnuok in I kikhawm.

[V2]
 Hung tau uo! Hung tau uo!
 Amah minin kikhawm hitiu;
 Sak, Thang, Sim leh Mal, hung tau uo!
 Van hinna an um dingin.

[V3]
 2. Belam, guolin Lal kawm apat I taimang,
 Gitloh hamling in ei nang;
 Ei vengpa'n puih kit dingin ei sam zing hi,
 Lunghei in, pakin zuon leng.

[V4]
 3. I pi leh I pu chana I deih penuh,
 Ei hawlin A hung tung tai;
 Zieziekchun pakchai tiu, ei Tanpa pha chuh,
 Vangsakna guoh hung zu hen.</lyrics>
<title>COME TO JESUS</title>
</song>